reviews.text: I was pleasantly surprised, they had really good food here! I'm a big supporter of peaches on pizza thanks to their seafood pizza. their pizza is worlds better than the pizza hut back in Canada.
Great place with reasonable prices. The food was also of top quality. The environment was also very friendly as well as having cozy furnitures.

Pizza hut is joke. Pricy and the quality of the pizza... 2 star. Only for the staff. If the staff I'll  start to speak English. I'll give the third star. Is the pizza you buy frozen at the supermarket. Well miky b pizza or even pizza express are way better..

1.Delicious pizzas are offered
2. Quick response
3. Not too crowded, with comfortable seats
Foods are ok, but the service need to be improved. Especially in Tung Chung Station.

reviews.text: 這裡到處都是溫泉水，隨處可泡泡溫泉浴，或者在溫泉池裡游泳……適合一家大小男男女女的渡假需要。
這是我最喜愛的食物,招呼又好。坐得舒服。正。
下午茶，可以一試。平均每人五，六十元
都非常多街坊捧場，不過記得帶件外套，空調好冷。
I was pleasantly surprised, they had really good food here! I'm a big supporter of peaches on pizza thanks to their seafood pizza. their pizza is worlds better than the pizza hut back in Canada.
